		<title>Do You Know What to Do When Your Goal Setting Fails?</title>
		<link>http://www.yourgoalsetting.com/do-you-know-what-to-do-when-your-goal-setting-fails/</link>
		<comments>http://www.yourgoalsetting.com/do-you-know-what-to-do-when-your-goal-setting-fails/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 23 Sep 2010 20:49:20 +0000</pubDate>
