		<title>Six Awesome Reasons to Set Goals</title>
		<link>http://www.yourgoalsetting.com/six-awesome-reasons-to-set-goals/</link>
		<comments>http://www.yourgoalsetting.com/six-awesome-reasons-to-set-goals/#comments</comments>
